<h2 align="center" class="style49"><font color="#00FFFF"> INTRODUCTION MANET NETWORK </font></h2>
<p align="justify" class="style8"><br>
  <span class="style14">The  MANET network &quot;Mobile Ad hoc NETwork&quot; are innovator network formed
  of wireless device (and then mobile) that are capable of communicate between their 
  carring out routing operation. In these networks there isn't need of infrastructure, 
  infact these aren't as technology telephony that has needed of antenna, receiver and trasmitter. 
  The ad hoc network are the sistem of data communication, founded on radio trasmission where 
  the device communicate on wireless canal, without centealized help. </span></p>
<p align="justify" class="style14">The Manet network are founded on concept Peer-to-Peer (P2P), where the peer are normal personal computer or PDA or laptop etc...The architecture P2P is an architecture where the peer can to share capability of computation, any type of resource, whitout the use of central server.The fulcrum of architecture P2P is the lack of central server that manages the connection and resource.This tecnology creates a network &quot;point-to-multipoint&quot; among device equals that behave, in some case or as client or as server. <br>
  A Manet network is a temporary network, without access point, that doesn't come preconfigure, but forms for only presence of a few device in particular territory. </p>
